               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17840114-63-cd337" type="crimeDate">2d of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840114-63-off336 t17840114-63-cd337"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840114-63-off338 t17840114-63-cd337"></join> last, four gold mourning rings, value 20 s. one other gold ring, value 5 s. one brilliant diamond ring set in gold, value 10 l. a silver egg, value 3 s. a mouning ring with a stone and two brilliants set therein, value 10 s. and one garnet ring set in gold, value 6 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17840114-63-victim684" type="victimName">
